    RelationalCommandCache.SelectExpression(
        Projection Mapping:
            Child -> Dictionary<IProperty, int> { [Property: Child.Id (int) Required PK AfterSave:Throw ValueGenerated.OnAdd, 0], [Property: Child.City (string) Required, 1], [Property: Child.Details (string), 2], [Property: Child.FirstName (string), 3], [Property: Child.IsDeleted (bool) Required, 4], [Property: Child.LastName (string), 5], [Property: Child.MiddleName (string), 6], [Property: Child.State (int) Required, 7], [Property: Child.StreetAddress (string), 8], [Property: Child.ZipCode (string), 9] }
            Date -> 10
            Id -> 11
            Reporter -> Dictionary<IProperty, int> { [Property: Reporter.Id (int) Required PK AfterSave:Throw ValueGenerated.OnAdd, 12], [Property: Reporter.Email (string) Required, 13], [Property: Reporter.FirstName (string) Required, 14], [Property: Reporter.IsDeleted (bool) Required, 15], [Property: Reporter.LastName (string) Required, 16], [Property: Reporter.MiddleName (string) Required, 17], [Property: Reporter.Phone (string) Required, 18] }
        SELECT c0.Id, c0.City, c0.Details, c0.FirstName, c0.IsDeleted, c0.LastName, c0.MiddleName, c0.State, c0.StreetAddress, c0.ZipCode, c.Date, c.Id, r.Id, r.Email, r.FirstName, r.IsDeleted, r.LastName, r.MiddleName, r.Phone
